c: 8
v: 52
t: "'inn ma nazal balmshrkyn yawmayidh sunnat allah fi eiqab altghat min al'umam alssabiqat min 'amthal fireawn walsabqyn lh, eindama kdhdhabu rusul allah wajahaduu ayath, fa'iina allah 'anzal bihim eqabh bsbb dhnwbhm. 'iina allah qawiun la yuqhr, shadid aleiqab liman easah walam yatub min dhnbh"